eiteam.esteemedinnovation.api.book

Class BookCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • eiteam.esteemedinnovation.api.book.BookCategory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BookPiece

    public class BookCategory
extends java.lang.Object
implements BookPiece
    A BookCategory is a set of BookEntries tied to a single concept. For example, the Helmet Slot category might contain various BookEntries for Helmet Slot upgrades.
